CodeDef oneline Filter
CodeDef oneline Description Truncate at first newline (CR or LF) or ASCII NUL
CodeDef oneline Visibility  public
CodeDef oneline Routine <<EOR
sub {
	my $val = shift;
	$val =~ s/[\r\n\0].*//s;
	return $val;
}
EOR
